The Fall Rate Alert will alert you when your glucose level is falling at or below the set rate.
The High Alert will alert you when your glucose level rises above the set level.
The Low Alert will alert you when your glucose level falls below the set level.
The No Readings Alert will alert you 20 minutes after your smart device stops receiving glucose readings from your sensor. You will not receive alerts, alarms, or sensor glucose readings.
The Rise Rate Alert will alert you when your glucose level is rising at or above the set rate.
The Signal Loss Alert will alert you when the app stops receiving glucose readings from your transmitter.
The Urgent Low Alarm will alarm you when your glucose level falls below %1$s %2$s.
The Urgent Low Soon Alert will alert you when your glucose levels are falling fast and will be %1$s %2$s in less than 20 minutes.
